{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01H6Zk1x3ACyH5C2CYGb3qDU","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→<!doctype html>\n     2→<html>\n     3→\n     4→<head>\n     5→\n     6→  <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n     7→  <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n     8→  <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n     9→  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    10→\n    11→  <title>PetClinic :: a Quarkus Framework demonstration</title>\n    12→\n    13→  <!--[if lt IE 9]>\n    14→    <script src=\"https://oss.maxcdn.com/html5shiv/3.7.2/html5shiv.min.js\"></script>\n    15→    <script src=\"https://oss.maxcdn.com/respond/1.4.2/respond.min.js\"></script>\n    16→    <![endif]-->\n    17→  <link rel=\"shortcut icon\" type=\"image/x-icon\" href=\"/images/favicon.ico\">\n    18→  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n    19→  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/css/petclinic.css\" />\n    20→\n    21→</head>\n    22→\n    23→<body>\n    24→\n    25→  <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    26→    <div class=\"container\">\n    27→      <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n    28→        <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"/\"><span></span></a>\n    29→        <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n    30→          <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n    31→        </button>\n    32→      </div>\n    33→      <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\" style>\n    34→\n    35→        <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n    36→\n    37→          <li class=\"active\">\n    38→            <a href=\"/\" title=\"home page\">\n    39→              <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    40→              <span>{msg:home}</span>\n    41→            </a>\n    42→          