{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NDUpj1sBUjWDyRhzw1CM8V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me also check the TemplateEngine to see if there's also an issue with how it wraps the error page template. From the output I saw earlier, the error response included \"Welcome\" text before \"Error\" text - that suggests the error template is being wrapped inside the base layout which already rendered the welcome content. Let me check the TemplateEngine:"}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1054,"cache_read_input_tokens":117914,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1054,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":206},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7877d114-a8cd-4b86-860b-21ca41dfcbd5","uuid":"99e77e17-4147-48e0-b668-afbc679df0e4"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_bdrk_01NDUpj1sBUjWDyRhzw1CM8V","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_bdrk_014bwccXYjqRnMSK7R51ANTg","name":"Read","input":{"file_path":"/home/bmcginn/git/scarf-latest/scarbench-evals/final/prompt_claude__whole_applications__petclinic__quarkus__jakarta/run_2/output/src/main/java/org/quarkus/samples/petclinic/system/TemplateEngine.java"}}],"stop_reason":"tool_use","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1054,"cache_read_input_tokens":117914,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1054,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":206},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7877d114-a8cd-4b86-860b-21ca41dfcbd5","uuid":"8d7ee2a1-7bd8-4a01-8112-b7174e61343b"}
{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_014bwccXYjqRnMSK7R51ANTg","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→package org.quarkus.samples.petclinic.system;\n     2→\n     3→import jakarta.annotation.PostConstruct;\n     4→import jakarta.enterprise.context.ApplicationScoped;\n     5→\n     6→import org.thymeleaf.context.Context;\n     7→\n     8→import java.util.Locale;\n     9→import java.util.Map;\n    10→\n    11→/**\n    12→ * CDI-managed Thymeleaf template engine.\n    13→ * Replaces Quarkus Qute templating with standard Thymeleaf.\n    14→ * Each template renders a body fragment, which is wrapped in the base layout.\n    15→ */\n    16→@ApplicationScoped\n    17→public class TemplateEngine {\n    18→\n    19→    private org.thymeleaf.TemplateEngine engine;\n    20→\n    21→    private static final String BASE_HEADER = \"\"\"\n    22→            <!doctype html>\n    23→            <html>\n    24→            <head>\n    25→              <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\" />\n    26→              <meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n    27→              <meta http-equiv=\"X-UA-Compatible\" content=\"IE=edge\">\n    28→              <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\">\n    29→              <title>PetClinic :: a Jakarta EE demonstration</title>\n    30→              <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/petclinic/webjars/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css\">\n    31→              <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/petclinic/resources/css/petclinic.css\" />\n    32→            </head>\n    33→            <body>\n    34→              <nav class=\"navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-dark\" role=\"navigation\">\n    35→                <div class=\"container\">\n    36→                  <div class=\"navbar-header\">\n    37→                    <a class=\"navbar-brand\" href=\"/petclinic/\"><span></span></a>\n    38→                    <button class=\"navbar-toggler\" type=\"button\" data-bs-toggle=\"collapse\" data-bs-target=\"#main-navbar\">\n    39→                      <span class=\"navbar-toggler-icon\"></span>\n    40→                    </button>\n    41→                  </div>\n    42→                  <div class=\"collapse navbar-collapse\" id=\"main-navbar\">\n    43→                    <ul class=\"nav navbar-nav me-auto\">\n    44→                      <li class=\"active\">\n    45→                        <a href=\"/petclinic/\" title=\"home page\">\n    46→                          <span class=\"fa fa-home\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    47→                          <span>Home</span>\n    48→                        </a>\n    49→                      </li>\n    50→                      <li>\n    51→                        <a href=\"/petclinic/owners/find\" title=\"find owners\">\n    52→                          <span class=\"fa fa-search\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    53→                          <span>Find Owners</span>\n    54→                        </a>\n    55→                      </li>\n    56→                      <li>\n    57→                        <a href=\"/petclinic/vets.html\" title=\"veterinarians\">\n    58→                          <span class=\"fa fa-th-list\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    59→                          <span>Veterinarians</span>\n    60→                        </a>\n    61→                      </li>\n    62→                      <li>\n    63→                        <a href=\"/petclinic/oups\" title=\"trigger a RuntimeException to see how it is handled\">\n    64→                          <span class=\"fa exclamation-triangle\" aria-hidden=\"true\"></span>\n    65→                          <span>Error</span>\n    66→                        </a>\n    67→                      </li>\n    68→                    </ul>\n    69→                  </div>\n    70→                </div>\n    71→              </nav>\n    72→              <div class=\"container-fluid\">\n    73→                <div class=\"container xd-container\">\n    74→            \"\"\";\n    75→\n    76→    private static final String BASE_FOOTER = \"\"\"\n    77→                </div>\n    78→              </div>\n    79→              <script src=\"/petclinic/webjars/bootstrap/5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\"></script>\n    80→            </body>\n    81→            </html>\n    82→            \"\"\";\n    83→\n    84→    @PostConstruct\n    85→    public void init() {\n    86→        engine = new org.thymeleaf.TemplateEngine();\n    87→        org.thymeleaf.templateresolver.ClassLoaderTemplateResolver resolver =\n    88→                new org.thymeleaf.templateresolver.ClassLoaderTemplateResolver();\n    89→        resolver.setPrefix(\"templates/\");\n    90→        resolver.setSuffix(\".html\");\n    91→        resolver.setTemplateMode(org.thymeleaf.templatemode.TemplateMode.HTML);\n    92→        resolver.setCharacterEncoding(\"UTF-8\");\n    93→        resolver.setCacheable(true);\n    94→        engine.setTemplateResolver(resolver);\n    95→    }\n    96→\n    97→    public String render(String templateName, Map<String, Object> variables) {\n    98→        Context ctx = new Context(Locale.getDefault());\n    99→        // Add all message keys as variables\n   100→        Map<String, String> messages = AppMessages.getMessages();\n   101→        ctx.setVariable(\"msg\", messages);\n   102→        if (variables != null) {\n   103→            variables.forEach(ctx::setVariable);\n   104→        }\n   105→        String body = engine.process(templateName, ctx);\n   106→        return BASE_HEADER + body + BASE_FOOTER;\n   107→    }\n   108→}\n   109→\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"7877d114-a8cd-4b86-860b-21ca41dfcbd5","uuid":"5e6625bd-e6db-4af3-a127-f72cb41c9271"}
